    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213990/extras/3cad3d71f1d7015225b32c0064e77104.poster.avif?t=1764811436\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213990/extras/3cad3d71f1d7015225b32c0064e77104.webm?t=1764811436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213990/extras/3cad3d71f1d7015225b32c0064e77104.mp4?t=1764811436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🚀 加入《My Last 20》任务！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>THE COMPANY</strong> 正在紧急招募勇敢的宇航员，参与绝密行动：<strong>《My Last 20》任务</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标：从<strong>混沌区域</strong>中尽可能多地提取<strong>太空代币</strong>，并且——<strong>只需坚持20秒即可生存！</strong><br>是的，只有20秒。这项任务还自带“死亡保险”。<br>你，敢接受挑战吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213990/extras/87d80a530591d4d7af0fff6ead4dc46f.poster.avif?t=1764811436\" width=800 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213990/extras/87d80a530591d4d7af0fff6ead4dc46f.webm?t=1764811436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213990/extras/87d80a530591d4d7af0fff6ead4dc46f.mp4?t=1764811436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 游戏模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌀 <strong>混沌区域（主线任务）</strong><br>在 <i>My Last 20</i> 的任务中，你将面对纯粹的街机疯狂——仅20秒！<br>陨石？奶牛？触手？每个混沌区域都有不同的敌人和难度，只有反应最快的宇航员才能活着逃出去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♾️ <strong>无尽街机模式</strong><br>在这个模式中，你拥有无限生存时间、强化道具和3个护盾。打破个人纪录，冲上排行榜顶端！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>硬核挑战</strong><br>完成一些疯狂的任务，比如“用炸弹烤100头奶牛！”，还能获得额外奖励！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>独特皮肤系统</strong><br>解锁奇怪又搞笑的角色皮肤：双层芝士汉堡、牛油果，甚至是橡皮鸭子！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213990/extras/76ab4a00ab3613bd0db980235b5664c1.avif?t=1764811436\" width=800 height=298 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >❓你是谁？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >头盔下的身份仍是谜团，但有一点是肯定的：<br><strong>你绝对不正常。</strong><br>你是唯一一个<strong>自愿报名</strong>参加这项任务并<strong>至少存活两次</strong>的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213990/extras/82b789e8b4577792e2cbe57b4506c405.poster.avif?t=1764811436\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213990/extras/82b789e8b4577792e2cbe57b4506c405.webm?t=1764811436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213990/extras/82b789e8b4577792e2cbe57b4506c405.mp4?t=1764811436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔑 游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>极度硬核挑战</strong><br>完成《My Last 20》的任务绝非易事。听起来只有20秒？试试看在陨石和奶牛之间生存！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚡ <strong>超快节奏玩法</strong><br>完美适合喜欢测试反应能力的玩家。反应慢一拍，就会被触手吞噬！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>疯狂像素画风</strong><br>现代与复古像素艺术的结合，加上各种独特又奇葩的角色，带来一场视觉上的宇宙旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>丰富的挑战内容</strong><br>游玩主线任务、完成疯狂挑战，或者在无尽模式中创造你的最佳生存时间！</p>",
